Use Case: Create an account.
Primary Actor: User
Scope:    Account Creation and Configuration.
Level: ! User goal
Brief:  A new member creates an account in the service after downloading the appropriate client.

Stakeholders:   --
Post conditions:
	Minimal guarantees - The user sees the webpage saying that email has been sent to his email id.
	Success Guarantees - User sees a webpage saying account creation successful.
	
Preconditions:
	The sign up link is displayed on the homepage of the website/app/software.
Triggers:
	The user clicks the sign up link/button.

Basic Flow:
	User clicks sign up.
	User fills form.
	User chooses secure password.
	User agrees to T&C and Privacy Policy
	User clicks captcha
	Verifies with OTP
	
Extensions:
	Choose secure, memorable password:
		Choose constraints of password.
			Character count.
			Character types.
			Restrict to English words only (not recommended)
			Restrict to custom dictionary only. (not recommended)
			Scramble the password
			
